Steffen,
comment.id is the unique id (tag <commentid>) within the Bugzilla installation for an comment. Here is what we get in the xml. <long_desc isprivate="0"> <commentid>2009</commentid> <who name="Mylyn Test">tests</who> <bug_when>2011-09-11 20:57:29 +0200</bug_when> <thetext>Description</thetext> </long_desc>
but commentNum is the local number within an bug and starts in every bug with one.
We need the commentNum for the "(In reply to comment #commentNum)" and the comment.id is used for set/reset the private flag of an comment.
